-- TMX Confirms It’s in Advanced Talks With LSE on Possible Merger
-- B y   H e a t h e r   B u r k e
-- 2011-02-08T22:21:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-08/london-stock-exchange-is-in-advanced-merger-talks-with-canada-s-tmx-group.html
  TMX Group Inc . said it is in advanced
discussions with London Stock Exchange Group Plc regarding a
possible merger of equals.   Current discussions contemplate an exchange ratio close to
the current market capitalization of London Stock Exchange Group
and TMX Group.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
